              <h1 class="_title post-title">Diversity Resources</h1>
        
      
  
  
  <p>UIC is among the top five most diverse campuses in the nation and a national leader among urban, public higher education institutions in providing access to underrepresented students. UIC is focused on eliminating disparities in health, education and economic opportunity. Community engagement is a centerpiece of UIC’s urban mission. Faculty, students and staff in every college work with neighborhood, foundation and government partners on a wide range of projects to improve the quality of life in metropolitan areas around the world.</p>
<p>Please click the appropriate link below to read more about the Diversity Resources available at UIC:</p>


